              <title>Role Playing and Collaborative Writing in Response to Literature</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7587</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7587</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>This cloud represents a narrowed down version of my previous project: what I want to focus on thinking about here is ways that collaborative writing can be used to generate a variety of responses to a text: essays, sequels, etc. These are activities that could be used in a MOOC or a more traditional class.&nbsp;</p>
<p>More specifically, my focus will be on higher education and adults since that is where my work is, and I want to begin by thinking about digital role playing as a form of collaborative writing.&nbsp;</p>
